{"tid":2169132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基因重構面孔助監控","createTime":"2020-08-22T08:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T09:54:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5413e599fd4df061e2c13bc2fef34687038f5e","tid":2169132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/Z7BEZTM4F5CFXOHYCCIXBOG3IA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FZ7BEZTM4F5CFXOHYCCIXBOG3IA%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=d78afd8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FZ7BEZTM4F5CFXOHYCCIXBOG3IA%2F&h=11ddf798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/Z7BEZTM4F5CFXOHYCCIXBOG3IA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n基因重構面孔助監控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Lg7eCMgU_n8toUrXUR6HpyRHFXU=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GHB5JAHEZJBRDN5WVDR4L2H7UM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLg7eCMgU_n8toUrXUR6HpyRHFXU%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGHB5JAHEZJBRDN5WVDR4L2H7UM.jpg&h=cc0f85de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁啟維<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】普及社區檢測計劃由中央欽點的三間大陸化驗所進行，來港協助檢測的內地支援隊員獲豁免《醫務化驗師規例》下的註冊要求，盡管政府多次重申化驗所不會取得接受檢測的個人資料，但醫管局員工陣線理事、註冊醫務化驗師梁啟維指出，港人憂慮無可厚非，因為現時檢測人士提供的樣本如鼻咽拭子，除帶有病毒外，「你撩到病毒都必定係會撩到人體嘅表皮細胞」，細胞中已包括整個人的基因資訊，只需要幾十微升已足夠做檢驗，「可以用個基因推算返你成個人，性別啊，甚至你個容貌係點樣。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：777拒向第三波68死者道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n化驗師憂難監管內地專家<br />\n<br />\n梁解釋，本地化驗師從讀書、工作，都着重職業操守，「一啲你唔應該睇、唔係因為工作上睇嘅嘢呢，你其實都係唔容許去睇」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年《紐約時報》就揭發，有中國科學家在國際發表的學術論文中，採用基因技術重構臉孔，可用於追蹤及監控，而研究的基因數據就是來自新疆一個叫圖木舒克的小城。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6a84862665a09b04d6f671cfda1448646bdaedae","tid":2169132,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"但個政府繼續愚民話唔會因為DNA知道你身份,但事實上透過DNA就真係唔知嘅,不過你有監控系統吖嘛,再加埋張新嘅殖民地身份證咪知囉."},{"pid":"55052fd63f7e8d38497e0d80089b2dd121640e0e","tid":2169132,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea3de284b34f0e54d68b81418cd0de4da5a369c4","tid":2169132,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 長毛象都係咁起返出嚟"},{"pid":"e1060531776a7b88227167c4b444e896865beac8","tid":2169132,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}